Package: bnsens
Type: Package
Title: Sensitivity analysis for discrete data in Bayesian networks
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ramanathan Ramsiya
Maintainer: Ramanathan Ramsiya <2420064R@student.gla.ac.uk>
Description: Tools for sensitivity analysis on discrete variables Bayesian networks. 
    Performs uniform, proportional, order-preserving covariation schemes.
    Performs CD-distance and Kullback-Leibler divergence for updating Bayesian network.
    Performs sensitivity function for probability of interest after update of network parameter.
